He can't do that. The law... No, that's English law.

251
00:15:06,847 --> 00:15:09,042
这个合同遵循苏格兰法
This contract was made under Scottish law.

252
00:15:09,207 --> 00:15:12,643
有个笨蛋没看出区别
Some idiot didn抰 realise the difference.

253
00:15:12,807 --> 00:15:15,799
