We're in the clear. Ah, yes.

254
00:15:15,967 --> 00:15:20,165
邮报也不能把50年代的事怪到你头上
Even the Mall can't blame you For a cock-up in the early'50s.

255
00:15:20,327 --> 00:15:22,363
