266
00:15:53,007 --> 00:15:56,795
没准是个大部门的常任秘书
He could be a Permanent Secretary running a great department,

267
00:15:56,967 --> 00:16:00,516
手握几十亿磅公款
responsible for spending billons of pounds of public money.

268
00:16:00,687 --> 00:16:05,078
