国防部文件啊      得了 这又不是机密
Well, Defence papers... Come on, this is not top security.

276
00:16:25,367 --> 00:16:27,278
听着 你竞选宣言里承诺
You made a manifesto commitment

277
00:16:27,447 --> 00:16:31,360
你会告诉选民真相 考验来了
saying you'd tell voters the facts. This is a test case.

278
00:16:32,367 --> 00:16:33,800
