这是承诺吗?      当然
Is that a promise?

282
00:16:42,727 --> 00:16:46,322
真的承诺 不是竞选宣言里那种
A real promise, not the sort you put in your manifesto!

283
00:16:46,487 --> 00:16:50,241
你就这毛病 别人答应你反而不信
The problem with you is you won't take yes for an answer!

284
00:16:51,247 --> 00:16:55,923
不然我们就写 "大臣出尔反尔"
Otherwise we do the feature about ministers ratting on manifestos.

285
00:17:17,851 --> 00:17:21,284
"政府玩忽职守 开发商大发横财"
"Developers' multimillion bonanza from Goverment error"

286
