Is that the lot, Humphrey?

287
00:17:32,967 --> 00:17:36,721
抱歉 似乎就这些了 大臣 谢谢
Oh, I'm sorry. That seems to be all, Minister, thank you.

288
00:17:36,887 --> 00:17:41,085
对了 汉弗莱 你看了今早的邮报没有?
Did you see that story in the Mall this morning?

289
00:17:41,247 --> 00:17:45,035
苏格兰海岛丑闻      我不记得
About the Scottish Island scandal. I'm not sure.

290
00:17:45,207 --> 00:17:47,277
有人犯了个错
About some cock-up somebody made

291
00:17:47,447 --> 00:17:50,200
30年前订错了租约
30 years ago about the terms of the lease.

292
00:17:50,367 --> 00:17:52,597
似乎是有这么一篇
I believe I did glance at it.

293
00:17:52,767 --> 00:17:56,680
4千万资产流失啊 这人可惨了
40 million down the tube! Somebody really boobed there!

294
00:17:58,807 --> 00:18:02,004
不是你的部门吧      当然不是
It didn抰 happen in your department? Absolutely not.

295
