I wonder who it was. That is something we shall never know.

296
00:18:06,727 --> 00:18:09,036
档案里会有吧?
It'll be on the files.

297
00:18:09,207 --> 00:18:11,846
事事都得归档 你总说的
Everything must be put in writing, as you always say.

298
00:18:13,127 --> 00:18:17,643
对 准有那么一份 可查起来就难了
Well... somewhere, no doubt, but it would take ages to search.

299
00:18:17,807 --> 00:18:19,399
没人会费那个劲
Not worth anyone's time.

300
00:18:19,567 --> 00:18:23,162
这你错了 邮报想做个大专题
You may be wrong. The Mall want to do a big feature.

301
00:18:23,327 --> 00:18:28,162
只等档案照30年规则解密 就几个星期
Papers are released under the 30-yearrule in a few weeks.

302
00:18:28,327 --> 00:18:31,319
我承诺让他们随便查
I promised them a free run of all the files.

303
00:18:34,087 --> 00:18:36,965
大臣      这没关系吧
Minister! it抯 all right, isn抰 it?

304
00:18:37,127 --> 00:18:40,676
没关系? 关系重大啊
All right? It most certainly is not all right!

305
00:18:40,847 --> 00:18:44,044
